      beam: '50\u00B0 / 60\u00B0 / 70\u00B0',
      foot: '<em>4-inch architectural cylinder &mdash; the most-specified Aura housing for general commercial perimeter. Datasheet at 30W default / 4000K. <code>12W = 1,550 lm</code> \u00B7 <code>18W = 2,270 lm</code> \u00B7 <code>24W = 2,980 lm</code> \u00B7 <code>30W = 3,660 lm</code>. Per-CCT variance and polar plots arrive with the IES bundle.</em>',
